text: Jan Koum (Ukrainian: Ян Кум; born February 24, 1976) is a Ukrainian American entrepreneur and computer programmer. He is the co-founder and was the CEO of WhatsApp. == Early life and career == Koum was born in Kyiv, Ukraine. He was raised and grew up in Fastiv, outside Kyiv, and moved with his mother and grandmother to Mountain View, California. ==References== Category:Living people Category:People from Atherton, California Category:Businesspeople from California Category:1976 births Category:Ukrainian businesspeople Category:Naturalized citizens of the United States
